text:
I'm creating a table module for a theme. This module has a repeater for multiple tables. Within each table there is a table heading and a specification row repeater (to build out the rows and columns for that table).

How do I define the context variable as an array in the section so each page can have their own table arrays?

Example Data:
  spec_table=[ {
          "spec_row" : [ {
            "spec_label" : "Item  1",
            "spec_value" : "Value"
          }, {
            "spec_label" : "Item 2",
            "spec_value" : "Value "
          }, {
            "spec_label" : "Item 3",
            "spec_value" : "Value"
          }, {
            "spec_label" : "Item 4",
            "spec_value" : "Value"
          } ],
          "table_heading" : "Table 1"
        }, {
          "spec_row" : [ {
            "spec_label" : "Item  1",
            "spec_value" : "Value"
          }, {
            "spec_label" : "Item 2",
            "spec_value" : "Value "
          }, {
            "spec_label" : "Item 3",
            "spec_value" : "Value"
          }, {
            "spec_label" : "Item 4",
            "spec_value" : "Value"
          } ],
          "table_heading" : "Table 2"
        } ]

TIA!
